  <heading>UMIN (immediate)</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Unsigned minimum (immediate)</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction determines the unsigned minimum of the
source register value and immediate, and writes the result to the destination
register.</para>
    </authored>
  </desc>
  <operationalnotes>
    <operationalnote>
      <operationalnote_content>
        <para>This instruction is a data-independent-time instruction as described in <xref linkend="ARMARM_BEICCDDAB3">About PSTATE.DIT</xref>.</para>
